extendedInfo.description: The TravelExpert.US app offers the most comprehensive hotel booking engine in the world. Our app offers instant reservations at over 130,000 hotels and resorts worldwide. Each hotel property in our reservation system features thorough overviews, photos, reviews, maps and ratings. Our hotel booking engine is fed by multiple databases, and customers can search for their desired hotel by using diverse criteria including by star rating, hotel chain, amenities offered, proximity to landmarks, and many more options.Our latest growth in accommodations inventory includes thousands of additional properties in Europe and many other destinations, from the United States to the Middle East, Asia and beyond. These new properties include resorts, airport hotels, small independent properties, and boutique and luxury hotels. Download our APP for quick, anytime access to discount hotel rates around the Earth. Updated hotel deals daily. Follow us @TravelPointers on Twitter and Find Us on the Web at www.TravelExpert.US
